April 11, 2013

A “Wanted” poster for alleged shoplifters at Williamsburg’s Artists & Fleas market. This poster is so funny to me for some reason, maybe it’s because it’s shot at eye level in full view of the perps who obviously just don’t give a fuck. Maybe it’s actually some kind of Brooklyn hipster marketing campaign.

April 5, 2013

Saw this weird mock-MTA service alert in the uptown R/N train station at 8th street this morning. The site it advertises is some Polish site. A user on reddit found this recently created blog featuring a variety of MTA-LOTR themed posters. Something’s going on here….
